'''休·马尔科姆·唐斯'''（{{lang-en|Shawn Kenneth Richards}}，{{bd|1921年|2月14日|2020年|7月1日|catIdx=Downs}}）是一名美国电台、电视主持人，活跃于1940年代中期至1990年代末。他曾是[[吉尼斯世界纪录|吉尼斯世界纪录]]“出镜时间最长的电视人”，但后来被[[里吉斯·菲尔宾|里吉斯·菲尔宾]]超越。<ref name="nytimes">{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/arts/television/2020/07/02/hugh-downs-dead.html|title=Hugh Downs, Perennial Small-Screen Fixture, Is Dead at 99}}</ref>

他最初是一名电台主播，自1945年开始主持电视直播。他主持过的节目包括《杰克·帕尔今夜秀》（Tonight Starring Jack Paar，1957-62）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.atvaudio.com/ata_category_search.php?current_page=1&category=T&alpha=T |title=A Matchless Library Television Archive: 1946–1982 |website=atvaudio.com |access-date=2020-01-03 |archive-date=2020-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200103001506/https://www.atvaudio.com/ata_category_search.php?current_page=1&category=T&alpha=T |dead-url=no }}</ref>、《[[今天_(NBC)|今天]]》（1962-71） <ref>{{cite book |last1=Mink |first1=Eric |last2=Dolphin |first2=Laurie |last3=Brown |first3=Christian |editor1-last=Dolphin |editor1-first=Laurie |editor2-last=Brown |editor2-first=Christian |title=This is Today: A Window On Our Times |language=en |publisher=Andrews McMeel Publishing |date=2003-10-01 |isbn=0740738534 |page=xiii |url=https://books.google.com/?id=XC5oCPxkPtUC&printsec=frontcover&dq=isbn:0740738534#v=onepage&q&f=false}}</ref>、《Concentration》（1958-69）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://fiftiesweb.com/tv/concentration/ |website=fiftiesweb.com |title=Concentration |access-date=2020-01-01 |archive-date=2020-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200101213554/https://fiftiesweb.com/tv/concentration/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=ryan>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/?id=hLiAiSxao5wC&q=Hugh+Downs |last=Ryan |first=Steve |title=Classic Concentration: The Game, the Show, the Puzzles |page=13 |publisher=Sterling Publishing Company |year=1991 |isbn=9780806984681 |access-date=2020-01-07}}</ref>和《[[20/20_(节目)|20/20]]》（1978-99）<ref name=post>{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/1999/05/06/host-hugh-downs-to-leave-2020/ca432d48-d528-44fe-90e5-b13632e0081d/ |title=Host Hugh Downs To Leave '20/20' |author=Lisa de Moraes |date=1999-05-06 |work=The Washington Post |access-date=2020-01-04 |archive-date=2020-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200105021321/https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/1999/05/06/host-hugh-downs-to-leave-2020/ca432d48-d528-44fe-90e5-b13632e0081d/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>等。

==生平==
他出生于美国[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]][[阿克伦_(俄亥俄州)|阿克伦]]，父亲是一名名叫米尔顿·霍华德·唐斯（Milton Howard Downs）的商人，母亲名叫伊迪斯（原姓Hicks）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/85/Hugh-Downs.html#ixzz0y9EDOn00 |title=Hugh Downs Biography |website=filmreference.com |access-date=2017-01-13 |archive-date=2018-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180118123932/http://www.filmreference.com/film/85/Hugh-Downs.html#ixzz0y9EDOn00 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他曾就读于[[利馬_(俄亥俄州)|利馬]]的肖尼高中（Shawnee High School）、[[布拉夫顿_(俄亥俄州)|布拉夫顿]]的布拉夫顿学院（Bluffton College）和[[底特律|底特律]]的[[韦恩州立大学|韦恩州立大学]]，1941年自韦恩州立大学毕业。<ref>{{cite magazine |url=https://oira.wayne.edu/publications/pub-fact-book-1011.pdf |title=2010–2011 Fact Book |publisher=Wayne State University |page=61 |year=2010 |access-date=2020-01-04 |date= |archive-date=2020-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200309201120/https://oira.wayne.edu/publications/pub-fact-book-1011.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===电台工作===
1939年，他曾担任利馬WLOK的电台主播<ref name="Cat"/>，1940年进入底特律的WWJ工作。二战期间，他在1943年入伍[[美国陆军|美国陆军]]，此后又在[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]的WMAQ工作，1954年才离职<ref name="Cat">{{Cite book|editor-last=Rayburn|editor-first=John|page=256|title=Cat Whiskers and Talking Furniture: Memoir of Radio and Television Broadcasting|year=2008|publisher=McFarland|url=https://books.google.com/?id=79bOhN089foC&pg=PA56&dq=freeman+gosden#v=onepage&q=wmaq&f=false|isbn=978-0-7864-3697-2|accessdate=2010-09-15}}</ref>。离职之后，他在1955年至56年间于[[哥伦比亚大学|哥伦比亚大学]]读书。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.columbia.edu/cu/record/archives/vol22/vol22_iss10/record2210.22.html |title=Hugh Downs Hosts Appreciation for Popular Physicist Motz |author=Bob Nelson |year=1997 |website=columbia.edu |access-date=2020-01-04 |archive-date=2010-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100627233020/http://www.columbia.edu/cu/record/archives/vol22/vol22_iss10/record2210.22.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===电视工作===
[[File:Jack_Paar_Hugh_Downs_Jose_Melis_Jack_Paar_Tonight_Show_1960.JPG|thumb]]》上的[[杰克·帕尔|杰克·帕尔]]、唐斯和[[何塞·梅里斯|何塞·梅里斯]]]]
[[File:Hugh_downs_darren_Mcgavin_riverboat_1960.JPG|right]]]]
1945年9月，他在芝加哥的WBKB-TV上首次登上电视舞台<ref>{{cite news|title=Hugh Downs Logs In Most Hours on Screen|url=https://www.orlandosentinel.com/news/os-xpm-1986-03-19-0210030148-story.html|first=Noel|last=Holston|date=1986-03-19|accessdate=2020-07-02|newspaper=Orlando Sentinel|archive-date=2022-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220513135019/https://www.orlandosentinel.com/news/os-xpm-1986-03-19-0210030148-story.html}}</ref>。他后来回忆道，在此之前他还从没来没有见过一台电视机，也不知道电视业是否能发展下去<ref>{{Cite web |title=Hugh Downs, omnipresent television broadcaster, dies at 99 |url=https://www.msn.com/en-us/entertainment/entertainmentnews/hugh-downs-omnipresent-television-broadcaster-dies-at-99/ar-BB16gy1n |access-date=2020-07-02 |website=www.msn.com |archive-date=2020-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119054619/https://www.msn.com/en-us/entertainment/entertainmentnews/hugh-downs-omnipresent-television-broadcaster-dies-at-99/ar-BB16gy1n |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1954年3月，他前往[[纽约市|纽约市]]在[[阿琳·弗朗西斯|阿琳·弗朗西斯]]主演的《家庭》（The Home Show）中担任节目播报员<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.monitorbeacon.net/communicators.html|title=Monitor's Communicators|publisher=MonitorBeacon.net|accessdate=2010-08-10|archive-date=2016-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161025124451/http://monitorbeacon.net/communicators.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1957年年中，他担任[[杰克·帕尔|杰克·帕尔]]《[[今夜秀|今夜秀]]》的播报员。1962年由杰克·帕尔离开节目组，唐斯的工作也在当年夏天由爱德·赫利希（Ed Herlihy）替代。<ref name="Encyclopedia">{{cite book|title=Encyclopedia of Television|editor-last=Dearborn|editor-first=Fitzroy|editor2-last=Newcomb|editor2-first=Horace|publisher=Fitzroy Dearborn Publishers|year=2005|pages=2697|isbn=1-57958-411-X|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=CFXgj7a55agC&pg=PA1288&dq=ed+herlihy#v=onepage&q=ed%20herlihy&f=false|accessdate=2010-12-04|archive-date=2020-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200727000647/https://books.google.com/books?id=CFXgj7a55agC&pg=PA1288&dq=ed+herlihy#v=onepage&q=ed%20herlihy&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1958年8月25日，他成为游戏竞赛节目《Concentration》的主持人<ref name=ryan/>，1962年又称为《[[今天_(NBC)|今天]]》的主持人。1975年至76年间，他和[[芭芭拉·沃尔特斯|芭芭拉·沃尔特斯]]共同主持了电视节目《Not for Women Only》。此外，他还曾出演NBC的情景喜剧《笑弹总动员》（Car 54, Where Are You?）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tv.com/shows/car-54-where-are-you/catch-me-on-the-paar-show-90677/ |title=Car 54, Where are You? Season 1, Episode 11, Catch Me on the Paar Show |website=tv.com |access-date=2020-01-04 |archive-date=2020-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200708154842/http://www.tv.com/shows/car-54-where-are-you/catch-me-on-the-paar-show-90677/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

他在1977年至83年间主持[[PBS|PBS]]的电视节目《Over Easy》，期间获得了[[亨特学院|亨特学院]]的老年病学硕士学位。1978年至1999年退休为止，他主持了[[美国广播公司|ABC]]的《[[20/20_(节目)|20/20]]》，这也是他最为人所知的节目。<ref name=post/>

他在1984年被[[吉尼斯世界纪录|吉尼斯世界纪录]]评为“出镜时间最长的电视人”（共15,188小时）<ref name=orlando>{{cite news |url=https://www.orlandosentinel.com/news/os-xpm-1986-03-19-0210030148-story.html |title=Hugh Downs Logs In Most Hours On Screen |last=Holston |first=Noel |work=The Orlando Sentinel |date=1986-03-19 |access-date=2020-01-04 |archive-date=2022-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220513135019/https://www.orlandosentinel.com/news/os-xpm-1986-03-19-0210030148-story.html }}</ref>，但2003年被[[里吉斯·菲尔宾|里吉斯·菲尔宾]]超越<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/most-hours-on-us-television?fb_comment_id=885667214798114_1007455985952569 |title=Most hours on US television |website=guinnessworldrecords.com |access-date=2020-01-04 |archive-date=2022-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516141601/https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/most-hours-on-us-television?fb_comment_id=885667214798114_1007455985952569 }}</ref>。

2007年10月13日，他成为最早入选[[拉斯维加斯|拉斯维加斯]]美国电视游戏竞技节目名人堂（American TV Game Show Hall of Fame）的人物之一<ref name=latimes1>{{cite news |url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2007-oct-11-wk-quick11.s5-story.html |title=Game shows get hall of fame |author=Staff Writer |work=Los Angeles Times |date=2007-10-11 |access-date=2020-01-04 |archive-date=2020-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710170334/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2007-oct-11-wk-quick11.s5-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年7月1日，他因心脏衰竭在[[亚利桑那州|亚利桑那州]][[斯科茨代尔_(亚利桑那州)|斯科茨代尔]]去世。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.abc15.com/news/national/american-broadcaster-hugh-downs-dies-at-age-99|title=American broadcaster Hugh Downs dies at age 99|publisher=ABC 15|date=2020-07-02|accessdate=2020-07-02|archive-date=2020-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200702174329/https://www.abc15.com/news/national/american-broadcaster-hugh-downs-dies-at-age-99|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Longtime broadcaster Hugh Downs dies at age 99 in Scottsdale home|url=https://www.12news.com/article/news/local/valley/broadcaster-hugh-downs-dies-scottsdale-home-2020-today-tonight-show/75-9d8d7aec-e445-4741-826c-286dd5cdca4b|date=2020-07-02|accessdate=2020-07-02|publisher=KPNX|archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703121304/https://www.12news.com/article/news/local/valley/broadcaster-hugh-downs-dies-scottsdale-home-2020-today-tonight-show/75-9d8d7aec-e445-4741-826c-286dd5cdca4b|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===其他===
[[File:Concentration_Hugh_Downs_1961.JPG|thumb]]
1961年至1964年间，他是[[联合国|联合国]]难民问题特别顾问<ref name=Newcomb>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=NUXIAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA755|title=Encyclopedia of Television|publisher=Routledge|date=2014-02-03|editor-last=Newcomb|editor-first=Horace|page=755|isbn=9781135194727|access-date=2020-07-08|archive-date=2020-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200702221019/https://books.google.ca/books?id=NUXIAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA755|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也是[[UNICEF|UNICEF]]美国委员会会长<ref name=Newcomb/><ref>{{cite news|title=Judy Collins, Hugh Downs win awards from UNICEF|url=https://www.deseret.com/1998/3/1/19366294/judy-collins-hugh-downs-win-awards-from-unicef|date=1998-03-01|accessdate=2020-07-02|newspaper=Deseret News|archive-date=2020-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200702212913/https://www.deseret.com/1998/3/1/19366294/judy-collins-hugh-downs-win-awards-from-unicef|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

他曾在1960年代为《[[科学文摘|科学文摘]]》撰写过一篇专栏，是[[福特基金会|福特基金会]]科学顾问、国家航天学会（National Space Society）成员及该学会前身国家航天研究所（National Space Institute）所长<ref>{{cite magazine |last=Downs |first=Hugh |date=1994-11-01 |title=Growing to a Position of Strength |url=https://space.nss.org/the-national-space-institute/ |magazine=Ad Astra |publisher=National Space Society |access-date=2020-01-07 |archive-date=2020-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920113242/https://space.nss.org/the-national-space-institute/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

他是一名[[自由意志主义|自由意志主义]]者，反对[[毒品战争|毒品战争]]<ref>{{Cite book|editor1-last=Evans|editor1-first=Rod|editor2-last=Berent|editor2-first=Irwin|page=346|title=Drug Legalization: For and Against|year=1992|publisher=Open Court|url=https://books.google.com/?id=cat3z6wfYRsC&pg=PA348&lpg=PA348&dq=drug+legalization+for+and+against+hugh+downs#v=onepage&q=drug%20legalization%20for%20and%20against%20hugh%20downs&f=false|isbn=0-8126-9183-0|accessdate=2010-10-14}}</ref>，主张[[大麻合法化|大麻合法化]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.perkel.com/politics/issues/pot.htm |title=Marijuana: Telling Teenagers the Truth about Smoking Pot |access-date=2020-01-04 |archive-date=2020-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205112843/http://www.perkel.com/politics/issues/pot.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

